title: ADD_AUTHORIZED_PARACHUTE_PACK_MODEL
content:
0x2E86DEA5// AddAuthorizedParachutePackModel
void ADD_AUTHORIZED_PARACHUTE_PACK_MODEL(int modelNameHash);Parameters:modelNameHash: Name hash of the model to allow to be used for the player ped's parachute packReturns: None.Adds the given model name hash to the list of valid models for the player ped's parachute pack.
